00052 void CHPMultiDataFileReaderTest::testReadCN()
00053 {
00054         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataCopyNumberData e;
00055         ParameterNameValueType param;
00056         CHPMultiDataData data2;
00057         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00058         reader.SetFilename("../data/CHP_MultiData_file_cn");
00059         reader.Read(data2);
00060 
00061         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00062         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00063         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00064         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(CopyNumberMultiDataType) == 2);
00065         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 0);
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00067 
00068         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00069         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00070         param = *it;
00071         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00072         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00073 
00074         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00075         it = p.begin();
00076         param = *it;
00077         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00078         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00079 
00080     data2.GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 0, e);
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 10);
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.position == 11);
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00084         data2.GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 1, e);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 20);
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.position == 21);
00087         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00088 }

00090 void CHPMultiDataFileReaderTest::testRead()
00091 {
00092     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataExpressionData ex;
00093     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData gn;
00094         ParameterNameValueType param;
00095 
00096         CHPMultiDataData data2;
00097         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00098         reader.SetFilename("../data/CHP_MultiData_file");
00099         reader.Read(data2);
00100 
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00102         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00103         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00104         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 1);
00105         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00106 
00107     // expression
00108     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00109     data2.GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00110         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ex1");
00112 
00113     // genotype
00114     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00115     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0) == L"int");
00116     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1) == L"float");
00117 
00118     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00119         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 1);
00120         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 11.0f, 0.0001f);
00121         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn1");
00122     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00123     param = gn.metrics[0];
00124     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00125     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 1);
00126     param = gn.metrics[1];
00127     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00128     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 2.0f, 0.00001f);
00129 
00130     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, gn);
00131         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00132         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00133         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn2");
00134     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00135     param = gn.metrics[0];
00136     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00137     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 2);
00138     param = gn.metrics[1];
00139     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00140     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 3.0f, 0.00001f);
00141 }
